title: Deadly Premonition NTSC/U Xbox 360
description:
Deadly Premonition:

Region      : NTSC/U                Languages: English        
Size        : 1 DVD                 Genre    : Action Adventure         
Platform    : XBOX 360              Date     : 02/2010

About:

The story of Deadly Premonition begins with Special Agent Francis Morgan trying to solve a murder. It ends with him trying to prevent his own. Fight to stay alive in this action-horror saga that sends you to solve a crime in a small town ringed by soaring mountains. Morgan searches for clues in the murder of a beautiful young woman. His investigation leads him to a harrowing realization: her death might be the work of a serial killer. Surrounded by an array of bizarre locals in a town haunted by supernatural creatures, Morgan must choose to stay low-key or conduct his investigation with guns blazing.
